quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  7,179,"Walaqad thara/na lijahannamakatheeran mina aljinni wal-insi lahum quloobun layafqahoona biha walahum aAAyunun la yubsiroonabiha walahum athanun la yasmaAAoona bihaola-ika kal-anAAami bal hum adalluola-ika humu alghafiloon"
  7,180,"Walillahi al-asmao alhusnafadAAoohu biha watharoo allatheenayulhidoona fee asma-ihi sayujzawna ma kanooyaAAmaloon"
  7,181,"Wamimman khalaqna ommatun yahdoonabilhaqqi wabihi yaAAdiloon"
  7,182,"Wallatheena kaththaboobi-ayatina sanastadrijuhum min haythula yaAAlamoon"
  7,183,"Waomlee lahum inna kaydee mateen"
  7,184,"Awa lam yatafakkaroo ma bisahibihimmin jinnatin in huwa illa natheerun mubeen"
  7,185,"Awalam yanthuroo feemalakooti assamawati wal-ardiwama khalaqa Allahu min shay-in waan AAasaan yakoona qadi iqtaraba ajaluhum fabi-ayyi hadeethinbaAAdahu yu/minoon"
  7,186,"Man yudlili Allahu falahadiya lahu wayatharuhum fee tughyanihimyaAAmahoon"
  7,187,"Yas-aloonaka AAani assaAAatiayyana mursaha qul innama AAilmuhaAAinda rabbee la yujalleeha liwaqtiha illahuwa thaqulat fee assamawati wal-ardila ta/teekum illa baghtatan yas-aloonaka kaannaka hafiyyunAAanha qul innama AAilmuha AAinda Allahiwalakinna akthara annasi layaAAlamoon"
